#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Rayleigh distribution."
msgstr "从瑞利分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:3 of
msgid ""
"The :math:`\\chi` and Weibull distributions are generalizations of the "
"Rayleigh."
msgstr ":math:`\\chi` 和韦布尔分布是瑞利分布的推广。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:6 of
msgid "Scale, also equals the mode. Should be >= 0. Default is 1."
msgstr "尺度参数，也等于众数。应大于等于 0。默认为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:8 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``scale`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``mt.array(scale).size`` "
"samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"如果 size 是 ``None``（默认），当 ``scale`` 是标量时返回单个值。否则抽取 "
"``mt.array(scale).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:13 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:15 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:17 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:20 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized Rayleigh distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的瑞利分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:24 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:25 of
msgid "The probability density function for the Rayleigh distribution is"
msgstr "瑞利分布的概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:27 of
msgid ""
"P(x;scale) = \\frac{x}{scale^2}e^{\\frac{-x^2}{2 \\cdotp scale^2}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:29 of
msgid ""
"The Rayleigh distribution would arise, for example, if the East and North"
" components of the wind velocity had identical zero-mean Gaussian "
"distributions.  Then the wind speed would have a Rayleigh distribution."
msgstr ""
"例如，如果风速的东向和北向分量具有相同的零均值高斯分布，则风速将服从瑞利"
"分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:35 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:36 of
msgid ""
"Brighton Webs Ltd., \"Rayleigh Distribution,\" http://www.brighton-"
"webs.co.uk/distributions/rayleigh.asp"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:38 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Rayleigh distribution\" "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rayleigh_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:42 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:43 of
msgid "Draw values from the distribution and plot the histogram"
msgstr "从分布中抽取值并绘制直方图"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:50 of
msgid ""
"Wave heights tend to follow a Rayleigh distribution. If the mean wave "
"height is 1 meter, what fraction of waves are likely to be larger than 3 "
"meters?"
msgstr ""
"波高通常服从瑞利分布。如果平均波高为 1 米，那么有多少比例的波高可能超过 3"
" 米？"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.rayleigh.rayleigh:58 of
msgid "The percentage of waves larger than 3 meters is:"
msgstr "波高超过 3 米的比例为："

